@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lnpyik(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.51) / 0.50))
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = v1
    v1 = 0.44
    v2 = wp.abs((0.37 * (v0 + 0.61 * v2 + 0.94)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.71)))
    data[tid] = v0
